---
title: Edamame, Hemp & Kumara Dumplings with Sesame Fries, Asian Slaw & Japanese Dressing
description: Dumplings have so much variety to them that deciding on one is tricky. Let’s kick things off with a veggie option with edamame,
hemp and kumara packed into these little parcels. A Japanese dressing will hit the spot as a saucy accompaniment.
